description: Maintain accessible and deterministic reader UI behavior
globs: src/phraseframe/web/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

# Reader UI

- Browser playback must consume server-generated frame durations.
- Preserve keyboard, focus-visible, reduced-motion, and narrow-screen behavior.
- Keep source errors and export state available to assistive technology.
- Avoid remote fonts, trackers, CDNs, or document-content analytics.
- Warn rather than celebrate when pace exceeds 350 WPM.
- Keep JavaScript modules small and dependency-free until complexity justifies a build system.
